  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How much would a wedding at a 5 star hotel in Mumbai for 400 people cost? Websites shows per-plate cost, does this include venue rental charges?",
  "response": "The cost of a wedding at a 5-star hotel in Mumbai can vary significantly based on several factors, such as the hotel's location, the services and amenities included, the season, and the specific requirements of your event. However, I can give you a general idea of what to expect:\n\n### Per-Plate Costs\n- **Per-Plate Cost**: As of the last available data, per-plate costs at 5-star hotels in Mumbai typically range from INR 3,000 to INR 10,000 or more, depending on the menu and other inclusions. For 400 people, this means a total cost ranging from INR 12 lakhs to INR 40 lakhs or more just for catering.\n\n### Venue Rental Charges\n- **Venue Rental**: Some hotels include the venue rental charges in the per-plate cost if you meet a minimum guest or expenditure requirement. Others might have a separate venue rental fee, which can vary widely based on the size of the space and the luxury level of the hotel. This fee can range from INR 5 lakhs to INR 20 lakhs or more.\n\n### Additional Costs\n- **Decor and Design**: Depending on your preferences, decor can range from simple to extravagant, costing anywhere from a few lakhs to several tens of lakhs.\n- **Entertainment**: Hiring performers, DJs, or live bands will incur additional costs.\n- **Photography/Videography**: Professional services for capturing the event can also add to the budget significantly.\n- **Other Services**: Lighting, AV setup, event management, transportation, and accommodation for out-of-town guests can also add considerably to the expenses.\n\n### Total Estimated Cost\n- Given these variables, you might expect the total cost for a wedding at a 5-star hotel in Mumbai for 400 people to range from around INR 30 lakhs to several crores, depending on the specifics of your choices and needs.\n\n### Recommendations\n- **Direct Inquiry**: Contact the hotels directly to get detailed quotes. They can provide a breakdown of what's included in the per-plate cost and any additional charges.\n- **Package Deals**: Some hotels offer package deals that might include catering, venue, decor, and other services at a consolidated price, which can offer cost benefits.\n\nIt's always a good idea to plan according to your budget and explore multiple options before finalizing.",
